    "As an illustration, CNNs can be fed a sequence of student grades from numerous semesters to predict future grades Poudyal et al (2022).",
    "Moreover, analyzing student demographic, behavioral, and academic data, is another method for employing CNNs Akour et al (2020).",
    "In this situation, the CNN can be set up to discover the patterns and relationships between the input features and after that predict the chances of a student succeeding in a specific course or program.",
